       Tarantulas quickly unscrambles the codes. What did killfest think he 
was doing? This was thier ship, their home, they knew all the codes and all 
the tricks to this vessle. 
       "Begin to flood the exhaust. At any rate it will keep them locked in 
the bridge." Megatron ordered. The lock down Killfest ordered was deleted, by 
Tarantulas. 
       Quickly, toxic green gas began to fill the ships corridors, labs, 
rooms, brig, and every other nook and crany. Killfest was going to have to do 
better than that.

--part1_92.d130f14.275ab60e_boundary
